  "texts": [
    "https://doi.org/10.1038/s42256-023-00775-6",
    "Molecular property and binding mode.",
    "We proposed to test our model and baseline models using targets from DUD-E, because a notable number of experimentally measured active compounds were documented in this dataset.",
    "Specifically, there are over 20,000 active compounds and their affinities against more than 100 targets, an average of over 200 ligands per target.",
    "This allows us to analysis the similarity between generated molecules and known active compounds."
